Validate element IDs

validate_ees_id.Rd

Validate element IDs

Usage

validate_ees_id(element_id, level = "publication")

Arguments

element_id

ID for publication or a data set

level

ID level: "publication", "dataset", "location", "filter_item" or "indicator"

Examples

validate_ees_id(example_id("publication"), level = "publication")
